<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.1.7">
<l>tōṟṟō maṭaneñca memperumā ṉāraṇaṟkem</l>
<l>māṟṟāmai colli yaḻuvōmai nīnaṭuvē</l>
<l>vēṟṟōr vakaiyil koṭitā yeṉaiyūḻi</l>
<l>māṟṟāṇmai niṟṟiyō vāḻi kaṉaiyiruḷē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>As it is cruel against us who have shown [our] foolish heart</l>
<l>to our great lord Nāraṇaṉ [and] who cry, speaking of our lack of strength,</l>
<l>you in the middle, why, in the manner of a stranger, would you</l>
<l>stand in enmity for an aeon, oh intense darkness?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
